<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.csicop.org/si/show/carl_sagans_life_and_legacy_as_scientist_teacher_and_skeptic">Carl Sagan's Life and Legacy as Scientist, Teacher, and Skeptic</a>, <a href="/wiki/Committee_for_Skeptical_Inquiry" title="Committee for Skeptical Inquiry">Committee for Skeptical Inquiry</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.skeptic.com/reading_room/our-place-in-the-universe">A Tribute to Carl Sagan: Our Place in the Universe</a>, <a href="/wiki/The_Skeptics_Society" title="The Skeptics Society">The Skeptics Society</a></li>
</ul>
