<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Haunted_Land:_Facing_Europe%27s_Ghosts_After_Communism" title="The Haunted Land: Facing Europe's Ghosts After Communism">The Haunted Land: Facing Europe's Ghosts After Communism</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Tina_Rosenberg" title="Tina Rosenberg">Tina Rosenberg</a> (1996)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Ashes_to_Ashes:_America%27s_Hundred-Year_Cigarette_War,_the_Public_Health,_and_the_Unabashed_Triumph_of_Philip_Morris" title="Ashes to Ashes: America's Hundred-Year Cigarette War, the Public Health, and the Unabashed Triumph of Philip Morris">Ashes to Ashes: America's Hundred-Year Cigarette War, the Public Health, and the Unabashed Triumph of Philip Morris</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Richard_Kluger" title="Richard Kluger">Richard Kluger</a> (1997)</li>
